allah-loves-kindness-easy\/","url_meta":{"origin":11666,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Rifq: Allah loves kindness, making things easy","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 15, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mughaffal reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah is gentle and he loves gentleness. He gives for it what is not given for harshness.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani Al-Azimabadi said, \u201cAllah loves gentleness, meaning, kindness\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33813,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/11\/24\/intimacy-approach-kindness\/","url_meta":{"origin":11666,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Intimacy: Approach your spouse with kindness, gentleness","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 24, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Utbah ibn Abdu Sulami reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen one of you comes to their spouse for intercourse, let them cover themselves and not approach each other like two wild mules.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 1921 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Suyuti\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/11666","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":